            "text": "to modeling cross-lingual semantic similarity ( CLSS ) in context ",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "parent": 2,
            "text": "which requires only comparable data . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "parent": 1,
            "text": "The approach relies on an idea ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "of projecting words and sets of words into a shared latent semantic space ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
